comments:
Abolished 1.4.1939 and added to the parish of Plymouth. See 
    also Table 2, notes (a) and (b).

Abolished 1.4.1939 and divided between the parishes of Plymouth 
    and Bickleigh. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (b).

Renamed 28.12.1966 to become the parish of Sparkwell. See also 
    Table 2, note (a).

Abolished 1.4.1967 and divided between the parishes of Plymouth 
    and Brixton. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (d).

Abolished 1.4.1967 and divided between the parishes of Plymouth, 
    Brixton and Wembury. See also Table 2, notes (a), (b) and (d).

Created 28.12.1966 by renaming the parish of Plympton St. Mary. 
    See also Table 2, notes (d) and (j).

Abolished 1.4.1951 and added to the parish of Plymouth. See 
    also Table 2, notes (a), (b) and (c).

Abolished 1.4.1951 and divided between the parishes of Plymouth 
    and Bickleigh. See also Table 2, notes (a), (b) and (c).
